# Production host normalization — http → https, www → apex.
# Netlify evaluates the request host against these patterns.
http://burjuy.com/*       https://burjuy.com/:splat  301!
http://www.burjuy.com/*   https://burjuy.com/:splat  301!
https://www.burjuy.com/*  https://burjuy.com/:splat  301!

# When DNS for burjuy.com goes live, uncomment the lines below to 301
# the netlify.app host to the custom domain. Leave commented until the
# apex resolves, otherwise the site appears broken on netlify.app.
# https://anton-burjuy.netlify.app/*  https://burjuy.com/:splat  301!
# http://anton-burjuy.netlify.app/*   https://burjuy.com/:splat  301!
